WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.290
Clinical priorities: early recognition via cardiac MRI,

00:00:03.290 --> 00:00:06.580
vigilant arrhythmia surveillance at three and six

00:00:06.580 --> 00:00:09.870
months, guideline-directed heart failure therapy, and staged

00:00:09.870 --> 00:00:11.280
return to activity.

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:14.100
References are provided for further review.
